  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Amber Family Clinic is a new GP clinc in the vibrant area of Katong. We are dedicated to providing comprehensive and personalised medical services for patients of all ages. Led by Dr Wong who has almost 20 years of experience in clinical practice, we are committed to delivering high quality holistic care in preventive medicine, acute and chronic disease management, lifestyle medicine and weight management. Dr Wong also has special interests in Women's Health and Children's Health.</p>\n<p><em><strong>We are excited to annouce an opening for a Clinical Assistant to join our team!</strong></em></p>\n<p><u><strong>Role Description:</strong></u></p>\n<p>This is a full-time on-site role as a Clinic Assistant at Amber Family Clinic in Singapore.</p>\n<p>As a Clinic Assistant, you will be responsible for various administrative and patient service tasks to support the day-to-day operations of the clinic. These include managing patient appointments, maintaining medical records, handling phone inquiries, assisting with billing and payments, and providing support to the medical team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will play a crucial role in ensuring the smooth running of the clinic in delivering exceptional patient care.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Qualifications</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong      organizational and multitasking skills</li>\n  <li>Excellent      communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Attention      to detail and accuracy in data entry and record keeping</li>\n  <li>Proficiency      in computer skills and familiarity with electronic medical records systems</li>\n  <li>Ability      to work well in a dynamic environment with a team</li>\n  <li>A      friendly and compassionate attitude towards patients</li>\n  <li>Fluency      in English and proficency in other langauges is a plus</li>\n  <li>Prior      experience in a healthcare or medical setting is preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>What we offer:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive      salary and benefits package including medical benefits and birthday perks</li>\n  <li>Opportunities      for professional growth and development</li>\n  <li>Supportive      and inclusive work envrionment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have a passion to make a meaningful impact on the lives of our patients, we would love to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please contact Dr Wong for more details.</p>\n<p>Email <a href=\"mailto:drwongsk@gmail.com\">drwongsk@gmail.com</a> with the subject line \"Clinical Assistant Application\". Thank you!</p>",
